metadata.description:
👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 GUNZO-ZU YUKI KOYANO 👨‍👩‍👧‍👦

888 NFT collection by GUNZO-ZU YUKI KOYANO 👨‍👩‍👧‍👦

Our NFT is made up of the art pieces of Yuki Koyano's 'GUNZO-ZU'. Infinity (∞) derived from the concept of the work is represented by the number 8.Infinity, spiral, life and death, reincarnation, and universe are the core themes of Yuki Koyano and embody his work. In addition, it will be an NFT that is inseparable from the exhibition. You will be able to enjoy everything from digital to analog from various perspectives such as experiencing on the display, owning, creating a community, participating in exhibitions, etc. Let's start the future of going back and forth between Metaverse x Art x Exhibition from these 888 NFTs.
